  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together flour, sugar, and baking powder.",
    "Add in unsalted butter and mix until a dough forms.",
    "Press dough into a 9-inch square baking dish.",
    "Bake for 20-25 minutes or until lightly golden.",
    "While the crust is baking, mix sour cream, mascarpone cheese, honey, lemon zest, and lemon juice in a separate bowl.",
    "When the crust is ready, remove from oven and pour in the sour cream mixture.",
    "Return to oven and bake for an additional 25-30 minutes or until the filling is set.",
    "Let cool completely before cutting into bars.",
    "Serve and enjoy!"
